reviewText: I bought this for $5 and it was well worth it. Entertaining; with peeks into current stars in the confines of indy wrestling. Why not?

Excellent show. This was more than worth my money. Had a great time watching it. CM Punk is so brilliant as a heel. If your a wwe fan please check this out. you have to see Punks early work to understand. Just how good Punk really is. Colt was great. Spanky was wickly brilliant.  Just pick this up and watch.
